keyDecisions[4]:
  Dispatcher dynamic discovery via fs.readdirSync + dynamic import(); ENOENT-tolerant so CLI ships before checks land. Now picks up all 12 modules + instantiates classes.
  /loom-doctor render: glyphs only on TTY (process.stdout.isTTY); text labels (PASS|WARN|FAIL) always present.
  Bundle redaction: strips installSourceUrl AND doNotTrack at every depth; keeps channel, source, version fields.
  MigrationRunner singleton constructed lazily with env-based channel resolution (CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT set → plugin; unset → curl).

